In a world where a good diner is hard to find: Handy's Lunch is da bomb.  Reliable food and a great place to chat up Earl, his mom, the mayor, the UVM basketball team, and anyone else who walks in the door.  Participatory dining at its finest!  Tourists get free advice and the local down-low.  Get a lunch to go and hit the bike path. How many McHandys can YOUR favorite teenager eat??
